              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Free tiers of ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini (train on your data by default). Never use for sensitive information without opting out.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-3 bg-white rounded-lg">
              <span class="w-20 text-center text-xs font-bold bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800 py-1 px-2 rounded-full">MED RISK</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Paid tiers with opt-outs configured (ChatGPT Plus, Claude Pro, Gemini Advanced). Reasonable for general professional use.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-3 bg-white rounded-lg">
              <span class="w-20 text-center text-xs font-bold bg-green-100 text-green-800 py-1 px-2 rounded-full">LOW RISK</span>
